breakFast.title: Mixed Berry Cereal
breakFast.body: Our low fat, low carb mixed berry cereal has 14 grams of protein and just 120 calories per serving. This fruity cereal, bursting with the taste of mixed berries, is pre-portioned to ensure that you get the perfect balance between taste and optimal nutrition every morning (or any time you want a delicious snack). 5 packets of cereal per box.

breakFast.title: Chocolate Peanut Butter Cereal
breakFast.body: This high protein (15g/serving) chocolate & peanut butter cereal is just what you’re looking for. There’s no reason to skip breakfast because if you love cereal in the morning (or a snack), this high protein, gluten-free, cereal is a great mix of flavor and nutrition that will keep you coming back for more. Just 9 carbs, and suitable for anyone watching their weight

breakFast.title: Low Carb Granola – chocolate & caramel
breakFast.body: Our low fat, low carb mixed berry cereal has 14 grams of protein and just 120 calories per serving. This fruity cereal, bursting with the taste of mixed berries, is pre-portioned to ensure that you get the perfect balance between taste and optimal nutrition every morning (or any time you want a delicious snack). 5 packets of cereal per box.

breakFast.title: Traditional Oatmeal Cereal
breakFast.body: Want a great and filling low carb start to the day? Try traditional oatmeal the Blissful Wellness way. Now you can enjoy that great stick to the ribs filling oatmeal while getting high protein and low carb options. We dare you to tell us you can taste a difference!

breakFast.title: Pumpkin Spice Pancake Mix
breakFast.body: Pumpkin spice flavored pancakes anyone? Whether you call them flapjacks or crepes, with natural flavor and 15g protein in every serving, they’re a delicious and nutritious way to start the day! You can also use this batter to make delicious waffles if that’s what you’re craving.

breakFast.title: CarbQuick
breakFast.body: Carbquick is your all purpose low carb alternative baking mix. Use this to make biscuits, pancakes, waffles and all other baking needs. Enjoy the taste, and none of the guilt (or carbs!)

breakFast.title: Chocolate Chip Pancakes
breakFast.body: Low carb pancakes are a dream come true for those of us who want to lose weight without giving up the foods we love. This chocolate chip pancake mix is a low carb, yummy treat. Pair it with our sugar free pancake syrup.

breakFast.title: Blueberry Pancake Mix
breakFast.body:
The only thing better than blueberry pancakes, is low carb blueberry pancakes! You won’t believe how delicious our high protein blueberry pancake mix is–quick, easy, and perfect for anyone on a low carb diet. Try topping it off with one of our zero sugar pancake syrups. (7 Servings/Box) – Low Carb, Low Fat, Low Calorie, Sugar Free, Aspartame Free.

            High Protein – 15 grams Per Serving
            Sugar Free / Low Fat – 1 gram Per Serving
            Quick and Easy to Make
            Low Carb – 8g Net Carbs (Net Carbs = Total Carbs – Fiber – Sugar Alcohols)
            Made in USA

breakFast.title: Low Carb Oatmeal
breakFast.body: Try this low carb oatmeal for your next breakfast. It is nutritious, delicious, and easy to prepare. Only 100 calories, but 14 grams of protein and just 6 grams of carbs to keep you slim and trim, but energized throughout your busy day.

breakFast.title: Peaches & Cream Oatmeal
breakFast.body: Try one of our low carb oatmeals for your next breakfast. We have a variety of delicious flavors to choose from, so take a look and see what looks good to you.

breakFast.title: Apples & Cinnamon Oatmeal
breakFast.body: Our low carb, high protein (15g) apple and cinnamon oatmeal is a warm, delicious way to start your next breakfast. We have a number of delicious flavors to choose from as well, but this is definitely a customer favorite. You’ll feel like you’re back in mom’s kitchen, getting ready to head out to school on a brisk day.

breakFast.title: Maple & Brown Sugar Oatmeal
breakFast.body: Try our maple and brown sugar low carb oatmeal for your next breakfast. Tummy pleasing comfort is just minutes away.

luanch.title: Oriental Chicken Shish Tawouk
luanch.body: Devour our fresh marinated shish tawouk skewers that are ready-to-cook and grill! Made from hormone-free & grain fed chickens, these marinated chicken skewers are infused with our secret oriental marinade that is so deliciously flavourful! No preparation time needed, simply throw them on the grill and devour their juicy taste and texture. Serve with Gourmet Tahini Dip, Cooked Egyptian Rice and Roasted Vegetables for a scrumptious and easy-to-prepare meal!
luanch.cooking:
Preheat pan/grill and grease with some vegetable oil.
            Grill Shish Tawouk on medium high heat for 3 to 5 minutes per side.
            Serve with Pita Bread, Garlic Dip, Hummus Dip and a side of our very own fresh Taboula or Fattoush Salad.
luanch.ingredient: Chicken Breasts, 7 Spice, Italian Herbs, Cumin, Coriander, Garlic Powder, Coriander, Tomato Paste, Lemon Juice, White Vinegar, Corn Oil, Sugar

luanch.title: Frozen Herbed Chicken Schnitzel
luanch.body: Devour our fresh marinated shish tawouk skewers that are ready-to-cook and grill! Made from hormone-free & grain fed chickens, these marinated chicken skewers are infused with our secret oriental marinade that is so deliciously flavourful! No preparation time needed, simply throw them on the grill and devour their juicy taste and texture. Serve with Gourmet Tahini Dip, Cooked Egyptian Rice and Roasted Vegetables for a scrumptious and easy-to-prepare meal!

luanch.title: Spiced Chicken Shawerma
luanch.body: Gourmet's tender, perfectly marinated & delicious chicken shawerma is read-to-cook. We suggest serving it with gourmet toumeya, mixed pickles and parsley. Our chicken is sourced from premium Egyptian suppliers, they are hormone free and grain fed.
luanch.cooking:
Preheat pan and grease with some Vegetable Oil.
            Sear Spiced Chicken Shawerma on medium high heat for 10 to 12 minutes.
            Serve with a side of our very own Taboula or Fattoush Salad.
luanch.ingredient: Chicken Strips, lemon juice, garlic powder, yogurt, corn oil, 7 spices, harisa paste, garlic, salt, cumin, sugar, dry thyme

luanch.title: Fresh Shish Tawouk
luanch.body: tender and juicy shish tawouk is perfect for grilling. Cut into cubes from Chicken thighs. Simply season with salt & pepper and enjoy a light and delicious meal. We recommend serving with your preferred Gourmet Fresh Salad, Gourmet Roasted Vegetables and Gourmet's Dip It Classic Hummus Dip for an easy-to-prepare & scrumptious meal. Our chicken is sourced from premium Egyptian suppliers, they are hormone free and grain fed.

luanch.title: Zaatar Whole Chicken in Oven Bag
luanch.body: Our flavourful marinated whole chicken will make roasted chicken your family’s favourite! Marinated with premium Jordanian thyme, garlic, sumac and sweet pomegranate molasses makes it delicious. Our chicken comes in a oven-safe bag. Simply, place the chicken in the bag in a preheated oven to 180 degrees for 60 minutes. Carve the chicken in a plate, spoon the sauce in the bag on top and serve with Gourmet Mashed Potato or Gourmet Roasted Vegetables for a mouthwatering rotisserie-like meal! Our chickens are sourced from premium quality and sustainable suppliers. They are hormone-free.
luanch.cooking:
Preheat oven to 180C.
            Place whole chicken
            without removing the plastic oven bag
            in a large baking dish and poke 5 holes in the bag – This is to allow steam to escape during the cooking process.
            Cook for 45 to 60 minutes.
            Serve with our Gourmet Roasted Vegetables, Garlic Dip, Hummus Dip, and a side of our very own fresh Taboula or Fattoush Salad.
luanch.ingredient: Fresh Whole Chicken, Vegetable Oil, Jordanian Thyme (zaatar), Pomegranate Molasses, Garlic, Salt, Pepper

luanch.title: Zaatar & Garlic Boneless Chicken
luanch.body: Enjoy our tender & marinated boneless chicken, infused with aromatic zaatar and flavourful garlic. It is super easy to cook or grill and makes a perfect weeknight chicken dish. Serve with Gourmet Roasted Vegetables and your preferred ready-to-eat products from our handcrafted oriental specialities. Our poultry is sourced from the most sustainable Egyptian suppliers, and are hormone-free.
luanch.cooking:
Preheat oven to 200C.
            Place Boneless Chicken in a medium baking dish and cover with aluminum foil.
            After cooking for 25 minutes, remove aluminum foil and bake for 10 minutes until skin is crispy and golden brown.
            Serve with a side of our Garlic or Hummus Dip, our Gourmet Roasted Vegetables or one of our fresh salads.
luanch.ingredient: Fresh Chicken, Corn Oil, Garlic Powder, Onion Powder, Cumin, Thyme, White Vinegar, Salt, Black Pepper

luanch.title: Frozen Classic Chicken Schnitzel
luanch.body: Enjoy our Classic Chicken Schnitzel made with hormone free & grain fed chickens. Our delicious chicken schnitzel is coated in crispy breadcrumbs and infused with mild spices. Serve with a side of Lamb Weston french fries & sauce of your choice. Preparation: Defrost at room temperature for 10 minutes. Deep fry in hot oil over medium heat until crisp and golden all over.
luanch.ingredient: Fresh Chicken, Corn Oil, Garlic Powder, Onion Powder, Cumin, Thyme, White Vinegar, Salt, Black Pepper

luanch.title: Oriental Chicken Leg
luanch.body: These delicious bone-in chicken thighs are tastefully marinated and ready-to-cook. They are perfect for grilling or oven-baking to make the most delicious, juicy and moist flavourful weeknight chicken dinner. Serve with Gourmet Roasted Vegetables and Gourmet Coleslaw Salad for an effortless mouthwatering meal!
luanch.cooking:
Preheat oven to 200C.
            Place Chicken Thighs in a medium baking dish and cover with aluminum foil.
            After cooking for 25 minutes, remove aluminum foil and bake for 10 minutes until skin is crispy and golden brown.
            Serve with a side of our Gourmet Roasted Vegetables and some Baba Ghanoush.
luanch.ingredient: Chicken Thigh, Coriander, Cumin, Ginger, Nutmeg, Cinnamon, Clove, Turmeric, Chilli Powder, 7 Spice, Fresh Lemon, Fresh Garlic, Yogurt, Salt, Black Pepper

luanch.title: Creamy Macaroni & Cheese
luanch.body: Is there anything that says ‘comfort food’ like macaroni and cheese? The problem is, that on a low-carb diet, mac and cheese is usually a no-no. Not any more, though, because our new mac and cheese has only 150 calories, 16 grams of carbs per serving, but is chock full of 15 grams of protein. Trust us, you need this in your pantry asap. Seven servings per box.

luanch.title: Vegan Chicken Curry
luanch.body: If you like a little spice in your life, give our delicious vegan chicken curry a shot. With no added fats and carbs, our new vegan-friendly chicken curry is made from a textured vegetable protein that will leave you satisfied. Packed with 15g of protein, a mere 7 grams of net carbs, and only 120 calories. Add this selection to your dinner menu and enjoy the great taste of curry without the guilt.

luanch.title: Alfredo Chicken Pasta
luanch.body: Chicken Alfredo is typically a no-no while you are losing weight. An typical dish can have more than 900 calories, loads of fat, and an entire day of carbs. However, we’ve made a version suited for a weight loss diet. Now you can enjoy alfredo pasta with just 15 grams of carbs, and only 130 calories.

luanch.title: High Protein Creamy Chicken Pasta
luanch.body: Our light creamy chicken pasta has a comfortingly creamy and cheesy sauce with a scrumptious chicken flavor that you’ll love. Not only is this a delicious meal, but it is packed with 15g of protein to help you build lean, healthy muscle. Seven single-serving packets per box.
